  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db0\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dda\u0d9c\u0dd3 \u0d85\u0db1\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca \u0db7\u0dcf\u0dc2\u0dcf \u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Korean language teacher killed in highway accident",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Athurugiriya Traffic Control Center states that a luxury jeep carrying a Korean language teacher collided with a lorry loaded with tiles last night (23) at Sapugaskanda area at Kilometer 16 Dec. 1 on the outer ring road of Colombo.",
        "Githani Manel Priyanti (47), a mother of one, residing at Gonahena Road, Kadavata, Rammuthugala, died in the accident.",
        "The accident occurred when the lorry loaded with tiles was running from Matara towards Kadawata when the luxury jeep which was running behind in the same direction collided with the back of the lorry, police said.",
        "As soon as the jeep collided with the lorry, it became a pile of debris and the teacher was seriously injured beyond recognition, the police say.",
        "The police say that the accident took place about two kilometers from the Kadawatha exit interchange",
        "Police investigations have revealed that reckless driving and over speeding of the jeep driver was the cause of the accident.",
        "The lorry driver has been arrested and will be produced in court",
        "Investigations are being conducted on the instructions of Chief Inspector MS Ashoka Kumara, Station Commander, Athurigiriya Traffic Control Center."
      ],
